OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779214266
OL,3,CTwo arrested in Scotland on suspicion
OL,4,Cof Belfast murder
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested in Scotland
OL,7,Fon suspicion of the murder of a 51-
OL,8,Fyear-old in east Belfast.
OL,10,FNicholas Gordon was assaulted in the
OL,11,FHolywood Road area of Belfast on
OL,12,FTuesday, May 12, and died in hospital
OL,13,Fas a result of his injuries on
OL,14,FSaturday.
OL,16,FThe men, aged 25 and 31, were arrested
OL,17,Fin Scotland on Monday by officers from
OL,18,FPolice Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
