OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779214266
OL,3,CTwo arrested in Scotland on suspicion
OL,4,Cof Belfast murder
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Arrangements will be made for their
OL,8,Freturn to Northern Ireland where they
OL,9,Fwill be questioned by detectives from
OL,10,Fthe Police Service of Northern Ireland.
OL,12,F"Inquiries are ongoing."
OL,14,FA 24-year-old man and a 49-year-old
OL,15,Fwoman had previously been arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of aggravated burglary with
OL,17,Fintent to commit grievous bodily harm.
OL,19,FBoth have since been released on bail
OL,20,Fpending further inquiries.
